{"id":123433,"type":6,"name":"絕代雙驕 (1979)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/94/d0/123433_uStdV.jpg","summary":"　　因爱成恨的邀月公宫，追杀江枫与花月奴夫妇，二人却离奇中毒身亡，邀月一怒定下毒计，把枫之一双孪生儿子分开抚养，企图令亲兄弟长大后互相仇杀以解心头之恨。十年余年后，一对孪生长大成人，花无缺（石修）在移花宫中被邀月授予超卓武功，而小鱼儿（黄元申）只学得了诡计多端。二人不期而遇，并结成好友，结识了苏樱(米雪)，铁心兰(黄杏秀)等几位姑娘，发展了几段爱恨交缠的爱情故事。聪明的小鱼儿是怎样揭穿自己的身世及识破邀月的鬼计呢？","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>绝代双骄</li><li><span>原作: </span><a href=\"/person/16836\">古龍</a></li><li><span>监制: </span><a href=\"/person/16604\">招振強</a></li><li><span>主题歌演出: </span><a href=\"/person/16550\">羅文</a>「絕代雙驕」</li><li><span>主演: </span><a href=\"/person/16928\">黃元申</a>、<a href=\"/person/16931\">黃杏秀</a>、<a href=\"/person/16698\">石修</a>、<a href=\"/person/16514\">黃允財</a>、 <a href=\"/person/16455\">陳玉蓮</a>、<a href=\"/person/16451\">米雪</a></li><li><span>配角: </span><a href=\"/person/17787\">呂有慧</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>The Twins</li><li><span>集数: </span>17</li><li><span>开始: </span>1979-05-06</li><li><span>类型: </span>武俠劇</li><li><span>imdb_id: </span>tt0843183</li><li><span>编剧: </span>胡沙</li><li><span>编导: </span>邱家雄、招振強、伍潤泉</li><li><span>编审: </span>胡沙</li><li><span>外景: </span>英屬香港</li><li><span>制作公司: </span>香港電視廣播有限公司</li>","eps":[{"id":471857,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/471857","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":471858,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/471858","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":471859,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/471859","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":471860,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/471860","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":471861,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/471861","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":471862,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/471862","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"",